name: CyberKidz Club ID #3599 - Searching
description: CyberKidz Club member #3599 is out looking for the remaining unadopted CyberKidz. Though it's incredibly dangerous to go into the wastelands alone and without a weapon, #3599 walks without fear, relying primarily on a keen sense of smell, thanks to rogue vampire DNA that found its way into the genetic mix during the 3rd great gas war.
